SEARCH
Package gw.api.exchangerates

Class DefaultSearchCriteria

java.lang.Object
gw.api.exchangerates.DefaultSearchCriteria
All Implemented Interfaces:
SearchCriteria, Serializable
public abstract class DefaultSearchCriteria extends Object implements SearchCriteria
Abstract class that allows prescriptive extensions of exchange rates search criteria.

This class exposes the wrapped platform search criteria instance (FXExchangeRateSearchCriteria) and he default logger instance to be exclusively reused by subclasses.
